Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:31.30,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:38.26,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久很久 我一直将你的后背
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:42.43,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作我的依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:49.57,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来将自己身处的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.78,0:00:56.16,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作是临时的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:59.74,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避着 逃避着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:02.66,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃向梦想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:07.92,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抱住你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:11.88,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:14.80,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与想象中相反的单纯内里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:17.76,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都让那稚嫩的自我意识
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:20.72,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阵阵刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:29.19,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 拖着泥泞沉重的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:34.44,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过至少身体强悍 所以今天也微笑面对吧
